<p>The proud mother can be seen standing on one foot with her right arm reaching above her head, while in-between her two children.</p>

<p>Anja is stretching out on floor in front of her mom while Noah does a semi-split to her right. </p>

<p>A family where life begins and love never ends!!! ¿¿¿ ¿<?php echo e('@'); ?>elle_russia <?php echo e('@'); ?>anjalouise.a.m &amp; <?php echo e('@'); ?>noahphoenixx By <?php echo e('@'); ?>gregswalesart</p>

